OL,4,BVAR: Arsene Wenger urges referees to
OL,5,Buse pitchside monitors in Premier
OL,6,BLeague
OL,7, Ex-Arsenal boss Arsene Wenger wants the
OL,8, Premier League to end its resistance to
OL,9, the use of pitchside VAR monitors.
OL,11,FPremier League referees' chief Mike
OL,12,FRiley has cautioned against their use
OL,13,Fby on-field officials because of the
OL,14,Fadditional time delay it would cause.
OL,16,FThat goes against Uefa guidance and
OL,17,FWenger, Fifa's newly-appointed head of
OL,18,Fglobal football development, wants the
OL,19,Fleague to change its stance.
